title: Finished watching Good Omens
body:
I have the following observations:

* I fucking love watching David Tennant act

* This is not a coded queer love story, this is an extremely obvious queer love story

* Since it’s canon that Aziraphale and Crowley have been working…together/against each other since the beginning of human history, you can write Good Omens crossovers with literally ANYTHING

* Like, is Ten actually Crowley? Maybe. Would explain a lot.

* Also, we could perhaps reopen the question of what really happened at Reichenbach Falls and how many divine/demonic interventions were involved
